DESCRIPTION:Beyond the Sky is Your Limit A satirical wellness seminar gone 
 spectacularly off the rails. Meet Heidi and Julie\, Australia’s leading (
 self-appointed) health gurus - armed with crystals\, confidence and zero qu
 alifications. In their first ever “live podcast\,” they tackle deeply u
 nserious health questions like: Do potatoes cure ADHD? Should you nurture y
 our pubic lice? Were you a cow in a past life? Expect chaotic Q&As\, dubiou
 s visualisations\, rogue embodiment exercises and a dangerously high dose o
 f unsolicited advice. But when a ghost from their past crashes the seminar\
 , their friendship\, business and grip on reality begin to crumble. Are the
 y actually enlightened healers - or just two women in matching linen\, wild
 ly out of their depth?\nMore info: https://comedyatlas.app/comedy-atlas/eve
 nt/beyond-the-sky-is-your-limit-with-heidi-and-julie/
